# NOTE: the BMad modules' generated references/ and scripts/ are intentionally
# COMMITTED (not ignored). The BMad installer clones this repo but does not run
# `npm install`/`prepare`, so a plain clone must already be complete. They are
# still generated from canonical sources by `make build`; CI fails if they drift.

